An open letter to the Amiga Community

12/24/96

The past few years have not been kind to the Amiga Community.  Since the demise
of Commodore, the ownership and future of the Amiga has been continually
uncertain.  The only thing that has remained constant is the loyalty of Amiga
users.  It is with respect to this loyalty that we feel it necessary to let YOU
