have reached a standstill.  As a creditor of Amiga Technologies, QuikPak has a
vested interest in seeing the future of the Amiga handled properly.  To this
end, QuikPak has placed an offer in front of the German liquidator for Amiga
Technologies, and we are awaiting further information regarding this.

